''Halo: Kumenyana Kusinthika'' ndi masewera othamanga omwe osewera amachitiramo masewera mu 3D chilengedwe pafupifupi kwathunthu kuchokera kwa munthu [[First-person (video games)|woyamba]] .  Wosewera akhoza kuyenda ndikuyang'ana mmwamba, pansi, kumanzere, kapena kumanja.  Masewerawa amakhala ndi magalimoto, kuchokera ku jeeps zankhondo ndi akasinja kupita ku ndege zowonongeka ndi ndege, zambiri zomwe zimatha kuyendetsedwa ndi osewera.  Masewera amasintha kwa [[Third-person view|munthu wachitatu]] pamagalimoto oyendetsa galimoto ndi oyendetsa mfuti; anthu okwera ndege amawonetsa munthu woyamba.  Masewera a mitu mmwamba anasonyeza chikuphatikizapo "zoyenda lodziwa kumene kuli" kuti akaundula kusuntha ogwirizana, kusunthira kapena kuwombera adani, ndi magalimoto, mu utali wozungulira zina za oseŵerawo.  

